			<td><br>Currently the Vice President of Marketing for Revell, Michael Brezette has been involved in the marketing and product development of consumer products for over 25 years with companies including First Alert, Newell Rubbermaid, and Healthometer.  He has also previously owned a product design and engineering firm and has also consulted in strategic marketing and product planning for both Fortune 500 and smaller companies.  He has been a speaker on the subject of effective product planning for the Color Marketing Group, Illinois Manufacturer’s Association, and various corporations.  Mr. Brezette holds a degree in Packaging from Michigan State University.

